📍 Havasu Falls, AZ 

𝘋𝘪𝘴𝘤𝘭𝘢𝘪𝘮𝘦𝘳: Havasu, Mooney & Beaver Falls Are All Located 10-14 Miles (Each Way) Of Hiking Within The Havasupai Reservation And One MUST Obtain A Hiking Permit To Visit These Locations Through Their Reservation System On February 1st Of Each Year. 

This Was My Second Time Visiting This Area (First Back In 2018), But This Time The Permits Were Pushed Back 3 Years Due The Havasupai Reservation Being Closed To Visitors During The Covid 19 Pandemic. 

These Permits Were Always Extremely Difficult To Obtain And I Can Only Imagine Now With A 3 Year Wait List. If You're Fortunate Enough To Visit The Most Isolated Tribe In America Plus Witness This Incredible Example Of Mother Nature, Cherish Every Moment Of It 💙

Once Upon A Time In Arizona 🏜

#Havasupai #HavasuFalls #HavasuCreek #HavasupaiFalls
